episodes.title: We're Alive, A Preview of Things to come...
episodes.summary: We're Alive has reached 50 million downloads! To commemorate the occasion, here's a sneak peak at the upcoming continuations in the series. Be sure to check out the website www.werealive.com to see our web store re-opening with a brand new special poster!

episodes.title: We're Alive: Lockdown - Part 6 of 6 - The Finale
episodes.summary:
The finale for Lockdown is here! Stay tuned for more content from Wayland Productions, including our next mini-series "We're Alive: Goldrush"!
For updates on new episodes, follow us on social media, and join in on the discussion at http://www.werealive.com

episodes.title: We're Alive: Lockdown - Part 5 of 6
episodes.summary: The Lockdown CONCLUDES!!! Join us for the live video broadcast, streaming finale of Lockdown part 6: June 3rd LIVE starting at 6 pm PST on www.werealive.com . The finale will then debut on the podcast feed June 6th, 9am PST. So if you want to experience the finale with the rest of the fans, join in on the finale stream on Friday June 3rd! Have an idea on how it will all end? Join in on the discussion at http://www.werealive.com/forum/

episodes.title: We're Alive: Lockdown - Part 1 of 6
episodes.summary: We're Alive is BACK with Lockdown. Join us on this 6 part mini-series as we dive deep into Twin Towers Jail, and follow a small group of unlikely survivors as they struggle to find their way out. New episode weekly, Part 2 airs May 2nd!

episodes.title: We're Alive: Lockdown Preview
episodes.summary: April 25th we launch our next story called Lockdown, a side-story/continuation further into the world of We're Alive! Enjoy this teaser, the first 15 minutes of Lockdown.
